ZH: 我们在市区里有一个警察分局。
EN: We have a police substation in the city.
ZH: 请到最近的分局报案。
EN: Please go to the nearest police substation to file a report.
ZH: 这个分局负责处理盗窃案。
EN: This substation is responsible for handling theft cases.
ZH: 我们的分局设有紧急热线。
EN: Our substation has an emergency hotline.
ZH: 分局的办公时间是早上9点到下午5点。
EN: The substation operates from 9 am to 5 pm.
ZH: 分局的警官会帮助您找到失物。
EN: The officers at the substation will assist you in finding lost items.
ZH: 请到分局领取您的新驾照。
EN: Please go to the substation to collect your new driver's license.
ZH: 这个分局有一个特别小组负责打击毒品犯罪。
EN: This substation has a specialized team responsible for combating drug crimes.
ZH: 在分局里你可以咨询交通事故的事宜。
EN: In the substation, you can inquire about matters related to traffic accidents.
ZH: 我的违章罚单可以在分局缴费吗？
EN: Can I pay my traffic violation ticket at the substation?
ZH: 分局的目标是确保市民的安全和治安。
EN: The goal of the substation is to ensure the safety and security of the citizens.
ZH: 分局每天都会巡逻街区。
EN: The substation patrols the neighborhood every day.
ZH: 我可以向分局申请警察记录的复印件吗？
EN: Can I apply for a copy of my police records at the substation?
ZH: 出警车辆的修理和保养在分局的车辆管理部门进行。
EN: The repair and maintenance of patrol vehicles are conducted by the vehicle management department of the substation.
ZH: 分局主任昨天晚上参加了社区居民的安全会议。
EN: The director of the substation attended a safety meeting with community residents last night.
ZH: 这个分局有一个培训中心，为警察提供持续教育。
EN: This substation has a training center that provides ongoing education for police officers.
ZH: 分局的职员会定期与市民举行安全讲座。
EN: The substation staff regularly conducts safety lectures for the citizens.
ZH: 在分局的大厅里有一个接待处，您可以得到咨询和服务。
EN: There is a reception desk in the lobby of the substation where you can get information and assistance.
ZH: 这个分局是负责管辖本区域的主要警务部门。
EN: This substation is the main police department responsible for jurisdiction in this area.
ZH: 分局将举办一次关于防火安全的活动。
EN: The substation will hold an event on fire safety.
